<choice ><statement><p>double</p></statement><feedback><p><c>walkDogs</c> should return the number of dogs that are walked, so it should return a whole number</p></feedback></choice>
<choice ><statement><p>boolean</p></statement><feedback><p><c>walkDogs</c> should return the number of dogs that are walked, so true/false wouldn't work</p></feedback></choice>
</choices>
</activity>

