<choice ><statement><p><c>int dogsToWalk = DogWalkCompany.numAvailableDogs(hour)</c></p></statement><feedback><p><c>numAvailableDogs</c> is a method in the DogWalkCompany class and needs to be called on an object</p></feedback></choice>
<choice correct="yes"><statement><p><c>int dogsToWalk = company.numAvailableDogs(hour)</c></p></statement><feedback><p><c>numAvailableDogs</c> is a method in the DogWalkCompany class and needs to be called on an object (company)</p></feedback></choice>
